  "text": "How did the Confederation send this love and like precisely what did they do? I am rock. There dwell within the Confederation planetary entities who from are there planetary spheres that do nothing but send love and light as pure streamings to those who call. This is not in the form of a conceptual thought, but of pure and undifferentiated love.",
